WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 29]

02:50.240 --> 02:51.360
We came to the village

02:51.360 --> 02:53.150
to find someone.

02:53.150 --> 02:55.240
Has anyone else entered the village

02:55.240 --> 02:56.650
recently besides us?

02:58.710 --> 02:59.430
Well...

03:01.770 --> 03:02.850
My disciple.

03:04.430 --> 03:05.400
Master.

03:07.730 --> 03:08.780
Are you okay?

03:08.810 --> 03:09.540
I'm fine.

03:09.590 --> 03:10.520
Of course.

03:10.540 --> 03:12.460
How can I not be fine?

03:12.990 --> 03:15.250
It's all thanks to Ms. Luan Zhu for saving me yesterday.

03:15.280 --> 03:17.530
She was also willing to take me in.

03:20.970 --> 03:23.010
Ms. Luan Zhu, thank you for saving my Master.

03:23.040 --> 03:24.480
I will protect

03:24.500 --> 03:25.750
anyone who enters Bodhi Village

03:25.780 --> 03:27.000
as long as they are kind.

03:27.020 --> 03:28.040
No need to thank me.

03:29.930 --> 03:31.650
Since Master has been found,

03:31.680 --> 03:32.910
we won't disturb you further.

03:32.930 --> 03:33.810
Goodbye.

03:34.970 --> 03:36.360
It's getting dark.

03:36.380 --> 03:37.620
Why are you leaving?

03:37.650 --> 03:38.850
The village is beautiful

03:38.870 --> 03:39.800
and has delicious food and wine.

03:39.829 --> 03:42.140
Accompany me here for a few more days.

03:42.500 --> 03:43.600
Divine Maiden, you won't mind

03:43.620 --> 03:45.870
having two more guests, right?

03:46.180 --> 03:47.500
Bodhi Village welcomes guests.

03:47.530 --> 03:48.800
You can stay as long as you want.

04:03.230 --> 04:05.690
Compared to your room,

04:05.710 --> 04:08.820
my room is too shabby.

04:08.850 --> 04:12.190
You youngsters have face.

04:12.620 --> 04:13.920
Not us.

04:14.150 --> 04:15.750
She treats us so well

04:15.880 --> 04:17.700
because of the Master of Bright Moon.

04:18.670 --> 04:19.910
No, it's not like that...

04:19.940 --> 04:21.600
What is it then?

04:21.630 --> 04:23.230
Your eyes never moved away

04:23.250 --> 04:25.200
from Luan Zhu just now.

04:36.620 --> 04:37.730
It's getting late.

04:38.080 --> 04:39.320
I'm so sleepy.

04:39.340 --> 04:40.550
I'm going to sleep.

04:40.620 --> 04:41.550
Master.

04:42.260 --> 04:43.260
I have something to ask you.

04:44.480 --> 04:45.310
What?

04:45.330 --> 04:46.060
Let's go.

04:46.470 --> 04:48.000
I'll open the door for you.

05:02.840 --> 05:03.710
Why does she have

05:03.730 --> 05:05.620
the bracelet of the woman in Jing Yuan's memory?

05:06.570 --> 05:08.800
Could they really have been a couple?

05:09.940 --> 05:11.410
I must get to the bottom of this.

05:11.760 --> 05:13.550
Otherwise, I can't explain it to Shuo.

05:16.650 --> 05:17.410
My disciple,

05:17.430 --> 05:19.180
I've told you

05:19.210 --> 05:20.970
men are untrustworthy.

05:21.000 --> 05:22.730
Since you're safe now,

05:22.750 --> 05:24.220
why didn't you tell me?

05:24.270 --> 05:26.460
Do you know how worried I was the entire day?

05:26.480 --> 05:28.000
Don't be angry.

05:28.030 --> 05:30.100
I was really in danger yesterday.

05:30.120 --> 05:32.080
Zhen Yu chased me halfway across the Eastern Continent.

05:32.110 --> 05:34.680
It was so dangerous this entire journey.

05:34.960 --> 05:36.690
Luckily, Ms. Luan Zhu saved me.

05:36.710 --> 05:38.630
I think Bodhi Village is very fresh.

05:38.659 --> 05:40.470
I forgot because I was having fun.

05:41.130 --> 05:42.820
How could Zhen Yu hunt you down?

05:42.860 --> 05:44.220
Lanling has a mountain protector barrier

05:44.250 --> 05:45.370
and he's injured.

05:45.390 --> 05:47.180
How could he break through the barrier?

05:47.210 --> 05:49.760
It's all my fault for being careless.

05:49.780 --> 05:52.659
I've collected all the spiritual herbs at the back of Lanling,

05:52.690 --> 05:53.450
so I thought

05:53.470 --> 05:56.150
to look for new herbs around Lanling.

05:56.190 --> 05:57.950
But not long after I exited the barrier,

05:57.950 --> 05:59.080
Zhen Yu found me.

05:59.110 --> 06:00.070
So I went east

06:00.070 --> 06:00.920
and ran here.

06:02.090 --> 06:03.690
Why did he want to kill you?

06:03.720 --> 06:04.830
You two have a feud?

06:05.610 --> 06:07.860
It's not a big deal.

06:07.890 --> 06:09.840
Many years ago, he came to me for divination

06:09.860 --> 06:10.780
and I lied to him.

06:10.810 --> 06:11.980
He got angry

06:12.000 --> 06:13.260
and came to give me trouble.

06:13.600 --> 06:15.780
It's just a trivial matter.

06:15.800 --> 06:16.900
Forget it.

06:17.600 --> 06:19.280
Lanling is the head of Eternals.

06:19.310 --> 06:20.510
Instead of hiding here,

06:20.530 --> 06:21.920
you should go back to Lanling.

06:22.070 --> 06:23.910
I can't go back.

06:25.570 --> 06:26.890
I've calculated

06:26.920 --> 06:28.650
that Lanling will have a catastrophe.

06:29.280 --> 06:30.280
A catastrophe?

06:30.710 --> 06:31.650
What catastrophe?

06:32.570 --> 06:35.030
I don't know exactly.

06:35.070 --> 06:37.790
Anyway, it's the best here.

06:37.810 --> 06:39.890
We have the protection of Divine Maiden Luan Zhu

06:39.920 --> 06:41.650
and Bodhi Village can't be found outside.

06:41.680 --> 06:42.530
This is the safest place.

06:42.560 --> 06:43.470
Safest, my foot.

06:44.310 --> 06:46.159
If you insist on staying here,

06:46.159 --> 06:47.690
I think I'll have a catastrophe.

06:47.710 --> 06:48.220
You...

06:48.250 --> 06:50.070
What catastrophe can you have?

06:50.659 --> 06:51.750
Did you really not see it

06:51.750 --> 06:53.190
or are you pretending?

06:53.210 --> 06:55.340
The Luan Zhu is coveting Fan Yue.

06:56.060 --> 06:57.260
Master, let me ask you.

06:57.280 --> 06:59.370
What exactly is this Bodhi Village?

06:59.400 --> 07:00.920
Who is Luan Zhu?

07:01.630 --> 07:02.720
I've never heard of

07:02.720 --> 07:04.430
this Bodhi Village before either.

07:04.430 --> 07:05.160
I only know

07:05.160 --> 07:07.210
people here call Luan Zhu the Divine Maiden.

07:07.230 --> 07:09.480
She has lived for a very, very long time.

07:09.510 --> 07:10.220
I heard that

07:10.270 --> 07:11.360
she's waiting for a lover

07:11.360 --> 07:12.800
from 60,000 years ago to return.

07:12.860 --> 07:13.970
60,000 years ago?

07:16.760 --> 07:19.050
if Luan Zhu has something to do with the Divine Race

07:19.080 --> 07:21.130
and Fan Yue has a Demon Lord's Divine Mantle...

07:22.110 --> 07:23.840
What if they really...

07:23.870 --> 07:25.020
What?

07:25.090 --> 07:26.480
Demon Lord's Divine Mantle?

07:26.510 --> 07:28.070
What do you mean?

07:55.600 --> 07:56.970
Since you came to see me,

07:57.150 --> 07:58.630
why don't you say anything?

08:00.940 --> 08:02.250
Who are you?

08:03.040 --> 08:04.900
What is your relationship with Jing Yuan?

08:05.400 --> 08:07.080
Have you really forgotten

08:07.100 --> 08:08.440
about our century together

08:08.900 --> 08:10.970
in the ancient Divine Region and the days

08:10.990 --> 08:12.390
in Xing Yue Pavilion?

08:12.570 --> 08:14.080
After the purple eyes returned,

08:14.100 --> 08:16.610
some images indeed flashed past my mind.

08:17.130 --> 08:18.080
But I knew

08:18.300 --> 08:19.820
those were Jing Yuan's memories.

08:20.750 --> 08:22.750
In those memories, there was a woman.

08:22.870 --> 08:24.310
I couldn't see her face,

08:25.180 --> 08:26.830
but I saw her bracelet.

08:27.540 --> 08:29.190
It's just like the bracelet on your wrist.

08:30.950 --> 08:32.880
So you came to me

08:32.950 --> 08:34.890
not because you thought of me,

08:35.179 --> 08:37.059
but only because of this bracelet.

08:39.080 --> 08:41.890
I don't want to hurt you,

08:41.970 --> 08:44.520
but looking at the current situation,

08:44.540 --> 08:45.940
you're in danger.

08:45.970 --> 08:47.610
All signs indicate

08:47.630 --> 08:51.260
Luan Zhu and Jing Yuan were a couple before.

08:52.120 --> 08:53.520
So you mean

08:53.550 --> 08:55.470
I'm the third party?

08:55.520 --> 08:56.960
I shouldn't be with Fan Yue?

08:56.980 --> 08:58.740
I didn't say that.

08:58.770 --> 09:00.270
The love between Luan Zhu and Jing Yuan

09:00.270 --> 09:01.930
was from 60,000 years ago.

09:01.970 --> 09:03.240
Times have changed.

09:03.240 --> 09:04.940
Now, you're the one Fan Yue loves.

09:04.970 --> 09:06.990
Of course I know that.

09:13.510 --> 09:14.850
But Disciple,

09:15.010 --> 09:16.850
because I'm your Master,

09:16.880 --> 09:20.050
I hope you can think some things through.

09:20.080 --> 09:22.070
Although you have spiritual power now,

09:22.090 --> 09:23.920
you're still a human.

09:23.940 --> 09:25.260
You can only live 100 years.

09:25.280 --> 09:26.820
You also said before

09:26.870 --> 09:28.860
Fan Yue has a Demon Lord's Divine Mantle.

09:28.890 --> 09:30.430
He has a long lifespan.

09:30.590 --> 09:33.310
Do you think you two are suitable for each other?

09:33.340 --> 09:35.190
Even if you are together,

09:35.220 --> 09:37.220
you'll only be together for decades.

09:37.240 --> 09:38.710
After you pass away,

09:38.740 --> 09:39.910
you can't control

09:39.930 --> 09:41.080
who he gets with.

09:41.870 --> 09:42.790
Do you think

09:42.790 --> 09:44.760
he and Luan Zhu should be a couple?

09:44.790 --> 09:46.680
I don't think so.

09:46.710 --> 09:49.180
I just hope you can be well.

09:49.240 --> 09:50.780
Don't hurt yourself.

09:50.810 --> 09:52.940
Even if Fan Yue isn't strong enough

09:52.960 --> 09:54.020
and falls for someone else,

09:54.040 --> 09:55.820
don't be too sad.

09:55.840 --> 09:56.630
Men...

09:56.660 --> 09:57.820
There are many men in this world.

09:57.840 --> 09:59.370
He's not the only one.

10:02.320 --> 10:03.640
60,000 years ago,

10:03.660 --> 10:05.300
you were the Demon Lord Jing Yuan.

10:05.330 --> 10:06.970
I was the Divine Maiden Xing Yue.

10:07.040 --> 10:08.710
We were together for 100 years.

10:09.200 --> 10:10.990
You promised me.

10:11.010 --> 10:12.370
You said you'll always...

10:18.180 --> 10:18.970
Never mind.

10:19.610 --> 10:20.640
You've forgotten

10:20.660 --> 10:21.940
everything.

10:21.970 --> 10:23.330
What's the point

10:23.350 --> 10:24.710
of mentioning "forever"?

10:25.780 --> 10:27.180
I don't remember things

10:27.450 --> 10:28.610
from 60,000 years ago.

10:29.800 --> 10:30.800
But I know

10:31.490 --> 10:32.980
Bai Shuo is the only one

10:33.520 --> 10:34.590
that I love now.

10:35.550 --> 10:36.850
I know.

10:37.140 --> 10:38.740
I saw her today.

10:39.480 --> 10:40.720
She's smart

10:40.750 --> 10:42.000
and spirited.

10:42.350 --> 10:43.860
Looking at her

10:43.970 --> 10:46.120
is like looking at my former self.

10:46.550 --> 10:48.010
But compared to me from before,

10:48.620 --> 10:50.430
she has more courage.

10:50.460 --> 10:52.180
The courage to love.

10:54.130 --> 10:55.800
She is a good girl.

10:55.860 --> 10:57.480
Since you chose her,

10:57.600 --> 10:59.180
you should keep going.

10:59.690 --> 11:00.890
Go back now.

11:00.980 --> 11:03.430
Just forget about this trip.

11:04.020 --> 11:06.390
Go back and live your life.

11:07.760 --> 11:08.780
It's late.

11:08.950 --> 11:10.080
Go back.

11:10.250 --> 11:11.780
Don't let her misunderstand.

11:24.490 --> 11:25.730
It's been 60,000 years.

11:26.450 --> 11:28.190
I finally found you.

11:28.930 --> 11:30.410
This time,

11:31.000 --> 11:33.640
I won't let anyone else have you.

11:36.750 --> 11:39.020
You finally thought it through.

11:39.300 --> 11:40.490
Returning to Lanling

11:40.520 --> 11:41.800
is the correct path.

11:42.130 --> 11:44.610
I'm very pleased.

11:47.320 --> 11:48.200
Could it be

11:48.200 --> 11:49.910
you came back to Lanling

11:50.150 --> 11:51.790
for another purpose?

11:54.750 --> 11:56.550
Since my parents died,

11:56.840 --> 11:58.840
you raised me like my father

11:59.120 --> 12:00.070
and taught me the magic

12:00.090 --> 12:01.240
and laws of the Eternals.

12:01.260 --> 12:03.410
I have never had any selfish intentions toward you.

12:03.440 --> 12:04.680
But today,

12:05.590 --> 12:07.790
I still want to ask you one more question.

12:07.900 --> 12:09.300
Were my parents

12:10.430 --> 12:12.180
really killed by demons?

12:12.410 --> 12:14.780
Are you questioning me?

12:14.820 --> 12:16.020
I dare not.

12:16.750 --> 12:18.030
But Xi has regained

12:18.030 --> 12:19.200
most of her memories.

12:19.220 --> 12:21.170
She said my mother met her before she died

12:21.190 --> 12:22.640
and asked her to tell me

12:22.750 --> 12:24.390
not to go back to Lanling.

12:24.420 --> 12:25.540
You believe it?

12:25.560 --> 12:27.010
I don’t want to.

12:27.760 --> 12:29.390
But Xi won't lie to me.

12:29.830 --> 12:32.130
The demoness is intentionally sowing discord.

12:32.150 --> 12:33.480
She should be condemned,

12:33.510 --> 12:36.220
while you fell into her trap!

12:39.530 --> 12:40.940
It's my fault.

12:42.250 --> 12:45.140
I shouldn't have sent you to the Cold Spring Palace.

12:45.890 --> 12:46.840
It's my fault.

12:46.860 --> 12:48.820
I should have called you back earlier.

12:48.870 --> 12:51.170
Now you've joined the demoness's side

12:51.190 --> 12:53.190
and regard Lanling as something lowly.

12:55.840 --> 12:59.230
My heart aches.

12:59.760 --> 13:00.550
I never meant that.

13:01.870 --> 13:02.890
But...

13:03.140 --> 13:04.370
It's just that I've never gotten closure

13:04.400 --> 13:06.000
for my parents' death

13:06.620 --> 13:08.440
I’ve never forgotten it.

13:15.920 --> 13:18.850
Since you are so obsessed with the truth,

13:19.600 --> 13:20.950
I am

13:21.080 --> 13:23.120
willing to take you to reinvestigate

13:23.120 --> 13:25.210
the cause of your parents' death.

13:25.230 --> 13:26.590
Tell me.

13:26.610 --> 13:28.370
What else did she see?

13:28.490 --> 13:29.880
Any other clues?

13:29.900 --> 13:31.390
She saw another person.

13:31.410 --> 13:32.530
Who?

13:33.250 --> 13:34.710
She stood far away

13:34.980 --> 13:36.880
and didn't see the person clearly.

13:37.100 --> 13:38.370
But she saw with her own eyes

13:38.400 --> 13:40.110
that the person hurt my mother with a sword.

13:40.260 --> 13:41.580
And that day

13:41.810 --> 13:43.830
was the day my parents' soul lanterns extinguished.

13:44.310 --> 13:46.580
What were that person's characteristics?

13:46.610 --> 13:47.860
What technique did he use?

13:47.880 --> 13:49.820
What did he do to your mother?

13:49.840 --> 13:50.870
Does she remember?

13:50.900 --> 13:52.860
Bai Xi was hit from behind

13:52.880 --> 13:53.920
and passed out.

13:55.090 --> 13:56.640
She doesn't remember much.

13:56.910 --> 13:58.150
How can these

13:58.170 --> 14:00.270
count as clues?

14:01.290 --> 14:02.740
Even if she didn't lie to you,

14:03.220 --> 14:05.260
it's been a long time.

14:05.290 --> 14:07.980
How can you be sure that she didn’t remember incorrectly?

14:12.590 --> 14:13.900
I see.

14:17.110 --> 14:18.620
I apologize

14:18.950 --> 14:20.210
and thank you, Master.

14:20.550 --> 14:21.860
You are busy with work.

14:22.050 --> 14:24.240
Don’t be too upset over my matters.

14:26.590 --> 14:27.880
Take care, Master.

14:32.410 --> 14:33.580
Goodbye.

14:36.370 --> 14:37.170
You...

14:37.440 --> 14:39.440
Are you really going back to her?

14:40.310 --> 14:41.420
Being with her

14:41.440 --> 14:43.010
will only harm you.

14:43.870 --> 14:45.980
She has been alone for too long.

14:46.310 --> 14:48.000
I want to go back to accompany her,

14:49.000 --> 14:50.770
no matter what is ahead of us.

15:28.890 --> 15:30.370
I went to see Luan Zhu.

15:31.400 --> 15:32.340
And?

15:32.500 --> 15:34.140
She said she's Goddess Xing Yue.

15:34.700 --> 15:36.150
60,000 years ago, she had a relationship

15:36.180 --> 15:37.530
with the Demon Lord Jing Yuan.

15:39.270 --> 15:40.360
What relationship?

15:41.570 --> 15:43.030
Vows as steadfast as mountains and seas,

15:43.170 --> 15:44.600
pledging life and death to each other.

15:45.020 --> 15:46.490
So you knew

15:46.710 --> 15:48.710
all of this before you entered Bodhi Village?

15:48.740 --> 15:49.960
Not entirely.

15:50.480 --> 15:52.110
I just saw some images.

15:52.400 --> 15:54.470
Jing Yuan put a bracelet on a woman,

15:54.970 --> 15:55.960
and that bracelet

15:56.730 --> 15:58.540
was exactly the same as Luan Zhu's.

15:59.190 --> 16:01.000
That's why I went to ask her.

16:02.940 --> 16:03.950
It seems that

16:04.410 --> 16:05.610
they were old friends.

16:06.340 --> 16:07.480
Old friends?

16:09.690 --> 16:11.290
So you were old lovers.

16:11.320 --> 16:12.540
I'm Fan Yue.

16:12.850 --> 16:14.650
I only have one lover.

16:14.850 --> 16:15.720
It's you.

16:17.750 --> 16:19.480
Your words sound nice,

16:19.820 --> 16:20.600
but you already have

16:20.600 --> 16:22.320
memories and images of her in your mind.

16:22.590 --> 16:23.840
You've started to avoid me.

16:23.840 --> 16:24.630
I avoided you

16:24.630 --> 16:26.150
because I didn't know who she was

16:26.150 --> 16:27.840
or why she appeared in my mind.

16:28.190 --> 16:29.280
Now I know.

16:29.310 --> 16:30.640
That's Jing Yuan's memory.

16:30.660 --> 16:31.750
It has nothing to do with me.

16:31.890 --> 16:33.250
I won't avoid you anymore.

16:35.240 --> 16:36.570
How do you prove that?

16:37.350 --> 16:42.390
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

16:41.900 --> 16:43.300
This way, I won't avoid you again.

16:44.860 --> 16:48.900
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

16:49.630 --> 16:54.060
♫You are my determined way home♫

16:53.350 --> 16:56.860
Actually, when Jing Yuan saved me back then,

16:54.550 --> 17:00.210
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

16:56.880 --> 16:58.830
he said one thing.

16:59.850 --> 17:01.850
Not all deities pity mortals.

17:00.850 --> 17:04.339
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

17:03.140 --> 17:04.430
You should be glad

17:04.690 --> 17:07.380
♫Let's never let go♫

17:05.260 --> 17:07.640
your eyes resemble theirs.

17:07.800 --> 17:12.880
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

17:09.819 --> 17:12.829
I didn't know who Jing Yuan was talking about,

17:12.940 --> 17:14.900
or whether they were a man or a woman.

17:14.390 --> 17:18.190
♫You are the blueprint of my life♫

17:15.050 --> 17:16.560
Now it seems

17:16.869 --> 17:18.569
it might've been Luan Zhu.

17:18.970 --> 17:23.410
♫The morning breeze and morning dew♫

17:23.849 --> 17:28.280
♫Let the tears celebrate♫

17:24.210 --> 17:25.930
That's just Jing Yuan's past.

17:26.790 --> 17:27.859
I, Fan Yue,

17:28.160 --> 17:29.170
will only

17:28.530 --> 17:31.630
♫We embrace each other in the sky♫

17:29.510 --> 17:30.500
love

17:30.950 --> 17:31.860
Bai Shuo

17:32.280 --> 17:34.210
in the past, present, and future.

17:32.470 --> 17:35.920
♫Let's never let go♫

17:36.590 --> 17:37.480
By the way,

17:37.500 --> 17:38.410
Master

17:38.440 --> 17:40.130
still refuses to leave Bodhi Village.

17:40.150 --> 17:41.740
I plan to stay with him for a few days

17:41.760 --> 17:42.760
to observe things

17:42.790 --> 17:44.960
and leave after confirming everything is okay.

17:44.980 --> 17:45.660
Okay.

17:46.720 --> 17:48.080
I'll stay with you.

18:12.210 --> 18:13.480
Welcome you two.

18:13.480 --> 18:14.510
Candied haws for you.

18:14.510 --> 18:15.220
Thank you.

18:28.160 --> 18:29.110
Smells so good.

18:32.460 --> 18:33.200
Sir,

18:33.200 --> 18:34.100
how much is this?

18:34.300 --> 18:35.350
It's free.

18:35.370 --> 18:36.420
In Bodhi Village,

18:36.450 --> 18:38.140
we have all kinds of good wine and food.

18:38.240 --> 18:38.880
Eat whatever you want

18:38.880 --> 18:39.760
and drink whatever you want.

18:39.780 --> 18:40.730
No money is needed.

18:40.760 --> 18:41.350
Miss,

18:41.350 --> 18:42.280
this is for free.

18:42.300 --> 18:43.150
Thank you.

18:43.180 --> 18:43.940
You're welcome.

18:47.400 --> 18:49.320
If all the people in the world

18:49.360 --> 18:51.080
could be like the villagers of Bodhi Village,

18:51.110 --> 18:52.190
that'd be great.

18:52.400 --> 18:53.920
Then people wouldn't starve or freeze

18:53.940 --> 18:55.870
and there'd be no famines.

18:56.190 --> 18:57.240
I just feel that

18:57.240 --> 18:58.260
this village is too perfect.

18:58.280 --> 18:59.040
What?

18:59.070 --> 19:00.400
You think something is wrong?

19:01.280 --> 19:03.470
Whenever things look too perfect,

19:03.620 --> 19:05.790
there's always something behind it.

19:06.350 --> 19:07.350
Fan Yue.

19:07.970 --> 19:09.410
After collecting the Five Contemplations

19:09.440 --> 19:10.810
and everything is over,

19:10.830 --> 19:12.500
we can find a place like this

19:12.530 --> 19:13.790
for the rest of our lives

19:13.820 --> 19:15.140
and live a life

19:15.160 --> 19:16.800
without conflict like them.

19:16.820 --> 19:18.310
That's my wish too.

19:18.880 --> 19:20.430
But what matters is

19:21.030 --> 19:22.070
being with you.

19:24.870 --> 19:25.630
Let's go.

19:29.410 --> 19:31.170
It's freshly cooked. Be careful, it's hot.

19:31.600 --> 19:32.470
Take it.

19:34.780 --> 19:35.700
Take care.

19:39.050 --> 19:40.470
Uncle Chong?

19:42.140 --> 19:43.580
Aunt Meng?

19:53.050 --> 19:54.310
Uncle, Aunt,

19:54.350 --> 19:56.350
I really missed you.

19:56.770 --> 19:57.790
Have you been here

19:57.790 --> 19:59.110
for the past ten years?

19:59.290 --> 20:00.290
Yes.

20:00.520 --> 20:02.000
We've been hiding here

20:02.030 --> 20:03.270
to avoid being killed.

20:03.810 --> 20:05.440
Who wants to kill you?

20:05.460 --> 20:07.310
Knowing the truth won't do you any good.

20:07.660 --> 20:08.310
All these years,

20:08.310 --> 20:09.670
we've been hiding here.

20:09.690 --> 20:10.870
We don't ask about worldly affairs.

20:10.890 --> 20:12.890
We don't even disturb Chong Zhao.

20:12.920 --> 20:14.400
Live your life

20:14.420 --> 20:16.380
as if we're already dead.

20:16.410 --> 20:17.780
No way.

20:17.800 --> 20:18.740
For the past ten years,

20:18.790 --> 20:19.750
Chong Zhao has never given up

20:19.750 --> 20:21.440
on investigating your real cause of death.

20:21.440 --> 20:23.380
He doesn’t believe you were killed by the scorpion demon.

20:23.400 --> 20:25.120
If Chong Zhao knew you are still alive,

20:25.150 --> 20:26.590
he'd be so happy.

20:32.930 --> 20:33.650
Shuo.

20:34.400 --> 20:36.090
Since they have their reasons,

20:36.110 --> 20:37.310
don't force them.

20:39.120 --> 20:41.090
I didn't have time to ask earlier.

20:41.120 --> 20:42.390
Who is this?

20:43.200 --> 20:45.090
This is the Master of Bright Moon Palace, Fan Yue.

20:45.110 --> 20:46.600
He knows Chong Zhao too.

20:46.950 --> 20:48.280
Bright Moon Palace?

20:48.940 --> 20:50.650
When we came here to live in seclusion,

20:50.680 --> 20:52.200
we hadn't heard of Bright Moon Palace.

20:52.600 --> 20:54.240
We haven't left Bodhi Village in ten years.

20:54.260 --> 20:54.870
It seems that

20:54.900 --> 20:56.530
we don't know the outside world anymore.

20:57.060 --> 20:58.170
Things have changed.

20:58.200 --> 20:59.170
Young people

20:59.190 --> 21:00.670
have their own world.

21:02.090 --> 21:03.050
Shuo.

21:03.080 --> 21:04.630
Since we've met again here,

21:04.650 --> 21:06.230
we should treat you well.

21:06.250 --> 21:07.880
I'll make you some delicious food.

21:07.910 --> 21:08.990
Come in.

21:10.870 --> 21:11.550
Come.

21:11.580 --> 21:12.580
Let's go inside.

21:22.960 --> 21:24.680
Do you think Chong Tai and Meng Ning are weird?

21:25.200 --> 21:27.150
Uncle Chong and Aunt Meng

21:27.810 --> 21:29.480
are the High Eternals of Lanling.

21:29.860 --> 21:31.580
Who could be after them,

21:31.770 --> 21:34.000
[To Chong Zhao]

21:32.090 --> 21:33.950
forcing them to live here in hiding?

21:34.440 --> 21:36.180
They don't even go see Chong Zhao.

21:36.320 --> 21:38.280
There must be something big behind this.

21:38.620 --> 21:40.550
Maybe they'll only tell the truth

21:40.570 --> 21:42.600
if Chong Zhao comes here.

21:42.750 --> 21:44.980
Besides, I've known Chong Zhao for ten years.

21:45.010 --> 21:47.240
I know how much he can’t let go of his parents.

21:47.510 --> 21:50.130
I’ll act on my own accord this time.

21:50.280 --> 21:52.540
I hope Chong Zhao can come here soon

21:52.710 --> 21:54.330
and reunite with his parents.

22:17.860 --> 22:18.780
[To Chong Zhao]

22:22.480 --> 22:24.550
[Zhao]

22:33.230 --> 22:33.800
[To Chong Zhao]

22:43.110 --> 22:43.960
Divine Maiden,

22:43.960 --> 22:44.830
we were wrong.

22:44.950 --> 22:46.540
We shouldn’t have let Bai Shuo see us.

22:47.260 --> 22:48.960
We were careless.

22:49.120 --> 22:50.570
Please forgive us.

22:50.650 --> 22:52.240
It's okay to make mistakes,

22:52.420 --> 22:53.590
but if you make a mistake,

22:53.620 --> 22:54.860
you should be punished,

22:54.880 --> 22:55.660
right?

22:59.710 --> 23:01.120
Please show mercy.

23:01.140 --> 23:02.820
We will hide ourselves

23:02.850 --> 23:04.410
so that Bai Shuo won't see us again.

23:06.540 --> 23:08.370
Since the show has started,

23:08.400 --> 23:10.110
how can we end it in a hurry?

23:10.440 --> 23:12.530
Not only should you let Bai Shuo see you,

23:12.550 --> 23:14.220
but also welcome your son Chong Zhao

23:14.250 --> 23:15.430
to Bodhi Village.

23:27.930 --> 23:29.280
I'm sorry.

23:29.390 --> 23:31.520
I was too excited just now.

23:31.540 --> 23:32.910
I shouldn't have hurt you.

23:32.930 --> 23:35.590
We are still a loving family.

23:38.070 --> 23:39.460
Will you still listen to me?

23:39.490 --> 23:40.950
We'll always be loyal to the Divine Maiden.

23:41.700 --> 23:43.390
Your son is coming.

23:43.420 --> 23:44.420
Do you miss him?

23:44.440 --> 23:45.670
No.

23:45.840 --> 23:47.740
He is your biological son.

23:48.250 --> 23:49.880
You haven't seen him in ten years.

23:50.170 --> 23:51.610
Of course you miss him.

23:51.630 --> 23:53.280
Not only that.

23:53.630 --> 23:56.040
You must also find more information about Bai Shuo

23:56.100 --> 23:58.710
from Chong Zhao.

23:58.830 --> 24:00.090
Understand?

24:02.610 --> 24:03.800
Yes.

24:06.190 --> 24:07.390
That's right.

24:20.580 --> 24:23.100
You've been restless since you came back from Lanling.

24:23.130 --> 24:24.000
You clearly think

24:24.000 --> 24:25.400
Jin Yao is hiding something from you,

24:25.950 --> 24:27.100
but you don't want to believe that.

24:27.530 --> 24:29.470
Master raised me.

24:29.850 --> 24:31.680
I shouldn’t suspect him.

24:31.700 --> 24:33.850
Zhen Yu also raised me.

24:34.050 --> 24:35.060
So what?

24:35.280 --> 24:37.630
If he raised you to use you

24:37.650 --> 24:38.740
and deceive you,

24:38.770 --> 24:40.330
making you view your enemy as your father,

24:40.350 --> 24:41.310
then this kindness

24:41.340 --> 24:42.450
becomes hatred.

24:45.360 --> 24:47.240
I will find out the truth

24:47.430 --> 24:49.210
and I won't have any more concerns.

25:00.020 --> 25:01.510
[I met Uncle Chong and Aunt Meng in the village.]

25:00.020 --> 25:01.510
[Zhao, when searching for Master, Fan Yue and I went chanced upon a village called Bodhi Village.]

25:09.080 --> 25:09.720
What's wrong?

25:09.740 --> 25:11.060
Shuo sent a message.

25:11.090 --> 25:12.610
She said my parents are still alive.

25:12.630 --> 25:14.750
They've been hiding in Bodhi Village all these years.

25:14.780 --> 25:16.070
Bodhi Village?

25:18.250 --> 25:21.220
[I met Uncle Chong and Aunt Meng in the village.]

25:18.250 --> 25:21.220
[Zhao, when searching for Master, Fan Yue and I went chanced upon a village called Bodhi Village.]

25:21.550 --> 25:23.150
I've been travelling everywhere all these years

25:23.170 --> 25:24.780
and I've never heard of this place.

25:24.810 --> 25:26.200
Shuo won't send random messages.

25:26.220 --> 25:27.600
She must have met my parents.

25:28.130 --> 25:30.700
I saw Aunt Meng get stabbed by a sword with my own eyes.

25:30.730 --> 25:32.120
Did someone save her

25:32.140 --> 25:33.260
after I became unconscious?

25:34.840 --> 25:36.240
No matter what,

25:36.260 --> 25:38.290
I want to set off to Bodhi Village immediately.

25:38.450 --> 25:39.990
You can stay here if you don't want to see Shuo

25:40.020 --> 25:40.850
and wait for me to return.

25:41.190 --> 25:42.080
I'll go with you.

25:44.240 --> 25:45.170
You...

25:45.360 --> 25:47.230
Have you figured out how to face her?

25:49.980 --> 25:51.430
I won't hurt her,

25:51.500 --> 25:53.780
but I will never admit that I am Bai Xi.

25:54.530 --> 25:55.850
I respect your decision.

25:56.300 --> 25:59.210
And I won't tell Shuo anything.

25:59.910 --> 26:01.550
But I still want to tell you

26:02.130 --> 26:04.650
that the fact that you are Bai Xi will never change.

26:04.780 --> 26:07.490
One day, you two sisters will reunite.

26:11.430 --> 26:12.280
Xi.

26:13.670 --> 26:16.060
Don't condemn yourself because of the past.

26:16.260 --> 26:17.820
You didn't want to do that either.

26:18.000 --> 26:19.690
You're a victim too.

26:20.020 --> 26:21.750
I believe Shuo will understand you

26:22.690 --> 26:24.060
and feel bad for you.

26:28.970 --> 26:31.340
I'll go pack up.

26:32.130 --> 26:33.500
Then we can go.

26:44.130 --> 26:44.910
Shuo.

26:44.940 --> 26:46.640
You said my parents are in this village.

26:46.670 --> 26:48.070
Is it true?

26:50.330 --> 26:51.960
Why did you bring her here?

26:53.920 --> 26:55.250
It was my idea.

26:55.280 --> 26:56.170
I don't want to

26:56.200 --> 26:57.380
hide anything from her anymore.

26:57.530 --> 27:00.180
Are you really going to be with her from now on?

27:00.210 --> 27:01.120
Yes.

27:05.910 --> 27:07.760
What happened to your parents is more important now.

27:07.780 --> 27:09.350
I won't confront her now,

27:09.780 --> 27:11.630
but one day,

27:11.730 --> 27:13.980
I will settle the debt that she owes.

27:16.600 --> 27:17.900
It's getting late.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.120
Let's go to the village first.

28:01.630 --> 28:05.020
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

28:05.480 --> 28:06.090
Father,

28:06.050 --> 28:08.490
♫The last moonlight♫

28:06.110 --> 28:06.700
Mother,

28:06.730 --> 28:07.940
I'm back.

28:08.460 --> 28:10.610
-Zhao.
-Zhao.

28:09.440 --> 28:13.060
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

28:14.230 --> 28:16.860
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

28:17.550 --> 28:21.560
♫In this life, at this time♫

28:21.130 --> 28:22.470
Slowly.

28:21.900 --> 28:25.370
♫I dare not look back♫

28:26.150 --> 28:29.370
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

28:27.000 --> 28:27.890
Father.

28:30.550 --> 28:33.600
♫On your path?♫

28:34.430 --> 28:37.470
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

28:34.800 --> 28:35.870
Mother.

28:38.130 --> 28:41.380
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

28:42.120 --> 28:43.980
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

28:42.480 --> 28:43.730
Zhao.

28:44.630 --> 28:46.460
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

28:45.490 --> 28:47.860
I knew you didn't die.

28:46.980 --> 28:49.700
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

28:49.020 --> 28:50.470
I knew it.

28:50.780 --> 28:53.830
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

28:51.220 --> 28:53.370
I've looked for you for so long.

28:54.000 --> 28:57.340
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

28:54.030 --> 28:56.130
I finally found you.

28:57.950 --> 29:00.270
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

29:01.000 --> 29:02.330
♫Time after time♫

29:03.090 --> 29:08.410
♫Oh, melancholy♫

29:14.570 --> 29:14.960
Come,

29:14.980 --> 29:15.740
Zhao.

29:15.770 --> 29:16.700
Sit down.

29:21.490 --> 29:22.560
Zhao.

29:23.430 --> 29:24.720
You've grown up.

29:25.870 --> 29:26.680
Father.

29:26.820 --> 29:27.690
Mother.

29:27.890 --> 29:29.370
What is this place?

29:29.610 --> 29:30.670
Why didn't you return

29:30.690 --> 29:31.930
to Lanling all these years

29:31.960 --> 29:33.750
or tell me you were still alive?

29:36.150 --> 29:36.960
Zhao,

29:37.490 --> 29:38.730
we're hiding here

29:38.760 --> 29:39.850
for you.

29:39.870 --> 29:40.950
For me?

29:40.980 --> 29:43.270
Back then, we were Eternal Envoys in Ning'an City.

29:43.300 --> 29:44.900
We often hunted down demons

29:44.960 --> 29:46.250
and made great contributions.

29:46.280 --> 29:48.160
We quickly became well-known.

29:48.270 --> 29:50.310
Not only were we regarded as a powerful enemy by the demons,

29:50.330 --> 29:53.240
but disciples of other Eternal sects

29:53.270 --> 29:55.200
were also jealous of us.

29:55.230 --> 29:58.060
Inevitably, grudges formed with time.

29:58.080 --> 30:01.450
After the last battle with the scorpion demon Qian Yin,

30:01.560 --> 30:04.290
your mother and I should have returned to Lanling to report.

30:04.310 --> 30:05.910
But on our way back,

30:05.940 --> 30:08.100
we were ambushed by other Eternals

30:08.120 --> 30:09.400
and got seriously injured.

30:09.430 --> 30:11.430
At that time, our power was greatly affected.

30:11.450 --> 30:12.930
When we fled to Bodhi Village,

30:12.960 --> 30:14.170
our eternal energy had shattered.

30:14.780 --> 30:16.930
Thanks to the master of this place, we were saved.

30:17.740 --> 30:19.260
When we woke up again,

30:19.280 --> 30:20.870
it was three years later.

30:20.900 --> 30:22.310
Your eternal energy shattered?

30:23.350 --> 30:25.450
No wonder your soul lantern went out.

30:25.480 --> 30:27.410
But a shattered eternal energy means death.

30:27.440 --> 30:29.200
What power does the master of this place have

30:29.220 --> 30:30.900
that can bring people back to life?

30:30.930 --> 30:31.850
Zhao,

30:31.870 --> 30:33.690
we can't say much.

30:33.780 --> 30:34.980
We can only tell you

30:35.000 --> 30:36.630
the master is very capable.

30:36.660 --> 30:37.900
Thanks to her,

30:37.920 --> 30:39.940
your father and I survived.

30:40.180 --> 30:43.090
We were going to find you as soon as we woke up.

30:43.240 --> 30:44.680
But we heard

30:44.700 --> 30:46.650
Lanling mistakenly thought we were dead

30:46.680 --> 30:47.680
and you

30:47.700 --> 30:49.970
were taken as a disciple by Sect Leader Jin Yao

30:50.310 --> 30:53.310
and being taken care of by Governor Bai Xun.

30:53.340 --> 30:55.990
What does it have to do with you not coming back to me?

30:56.510 --> 30:57.750
We have too many grudges

30:57.750 --> 30:58.960
and our cultivation has greatly decreased.

30:59.120 --> 31:00.330
If we appear,

31:00.350 --> 31:02.120
someone will take revenge on us.

31:02.570 --> 31:04.040
It's not good for you.

31:04.550 --> 31:05.550
Growing up under the protection of

31:05.550 --> 31:07.500
Sect Leader Jin Yao and Governor Bai Xun

31:07.520 --> 31:08.950
was the safest for you.

31:10.550 --> 31:11.580
Look at me.

31:11.880 --> 31:13.230
I was too busy talking.

31:13.420 --> 31:15.500
I forgot we have guests.

31:18.210 --> 31:19.880
Uncle, Aunt, don't be angry.

31:19.900 --> 31:21.580
I acted on my own this time.

31:21.600 --> 31:22.550
I brought Chong Zhao over

31:22.580 --> 31:23.820
without your permission.

31:25.380 --> 31:26.320
Shuo.

31:26.340 --> 31:27.760
Don't say that.

31:28.020 --> 31:29.130
Thank you.

31:29.430 --> 31:30.880
Thanks to you,

31:30.900 --> 31:32.780
our family is reunited.

31:33.700 --> 31:35.710
We were worried about nothing.

31:37.540 --> 31:38.320
Shuo.

31:39.250 --> 31:40.220
Xi.

31:43.810 --> 31:45.760
You must accompany me today

31:45.790 --> 31:47.120
and have a good time.

31:55.880 --> 31:56.670
Mother.

31:57.520 --> 31:58.840
She's not Xi.

31:58.860 --> 32:00.010
She is my friend,

32:00.040 --> 32:01.260
Fu Ling.

32:02.200 --> 32:03.400
I'm sorry, miss.

32:03.420 --> 32:04.730
You look kind

32:04.760 --> 32:06.170
and you came with Zhao.

32:06.200 --> 32:06.680
I thought you were...

32:06.680 --> 32:07.440
Ma'am.

32:08.420 --> 32:09.580
Is there anything

32:09.610 --> 32:10.460
I can help you with?

32:11.520 --> 32:12.490
You're a guest.

32:12.550 --> 32:14.030
How can I let you work?

32:14.050 --> 32:14.890
Have a seat

32:14.920 --> 32:15.710
and chat.

32:15.730 --> 32:17.520
I'll cook some delicious food for you.

32:18.610 --> 32:19.590
Sit down and talk.

32:19.590 --> 32:21.030
Make yourself at home.

32:40.550 --> 32:42.070
Do you have any doubts?

32:44.030 --> 32:44.920
No.

32:45.400 --> 32:46.680
What doubts can I have?

32:47.760 --> 32:48.240
Fu Ling.

32:48.260 --> 32:49.700
Fu Ling can't be Xi.

32:51.160 --> 32:52.580
If you have no doubts,

32:53.160 --> 32:54.960
why are you so eager to deny it?

32:56.470 --> 32:58.480
Actually, we did overlook one thing.

32:59.090 --> 33:00.260
For so many years,

33:00.370 --> 33:02.790
Zhen Yu only had two disciples.

33:03.200 --> 33:04.280
One was Qi Feng.

33:04.560 --> 33:05.520
The other was Fu Ling.

33:06.070 --> 33:08.280
Zhen Yu took away the Qi Feng on purpose.

33:09.120 --> 33:10.120
What about Fu Ling?

33:10.840 --> 33:12.430
Why did Zhen Yu

33:12.570 --> 33:13.850
keep Fu Ling by his side?

33:14.880 --> 33:17.210
Back then, Bai Xi was tricked and taken from the Governor's Mansion

33:17.290 --> 33:18.850
by Zhen Yu disguised as a Taoist.

33:19.500 --> 33:21.540
You saw her in Qi Feng's memories too.

33:22.460 --> 33:24.330
Since Zhen Yu tried so hard to take her,

33:24.350 --> 33:26.080
he wouldn’t have killed her for no reason.

33:26.310 --> 33:27.400
If he didn't kill her,

33:27.670 --> 33:29.160
but she disappeared,

33:30.520 --> 33:32.190
then there is another possibility.

33:33.070 --> 33:35.070
She didn't stay in the Cold Spring Palace

33:35.070 --> 33:36.270
as Bai Xi

33:37.440 --> 33:37.830
but...

33:37.830 --> 33:39.240
It's just a coincidence.

33:41.840 --> 33:43.050
Xi is a human.

33:43.820 --> 33:45.390
Fu Ling is a demon.

33:46.230 --> 33:48.090
She can't be Xi.

33:49.570 --> 33:50.620
Impossible.

33:52.990 --> 33:53.760
Impossible.

34:07.830 --> 34:09.000
There's one more

34:09.000 --> 34:10.480
new guest than expected.

34:11.199 --> 34:12.360
Divine Maiden, don’t worry.

34:12.380 --> 34:14.480
Chong Zhao asked many questions today,

34:14.510 --> 34:16.389
but we explained everything.

34:16.409 --> 34:18.110
They shouldn't suspect anything.

34:19.739 --> 34:21.239
"Shouldn't."

34:23.750 --> 34:25.750
The four of them are smart.

34:25.770 --> 34:28.270
It's normal even if they have suspicions.

34:31.159 --> 34:32.469
Don't be afraid.

34:32.500 --> 34:34.120
I'm not angry.

34:36.130 --> 34:38.420
Since they've entered Bodhi Village,

34:38.500 --> 34:40.750
I won't let them out again.

34:41.370 --> 34:44.699
None can leave.

35:06.110 --> 35:06.780
Wait.

35:08.790 --> 35:09.910
I have something to ask you.

35:11.110 --> 35:11.960
I have nothing to say to you.

35:11.960 --> 35:13.630
Why did you go to the Cold Spring Palace?

35:15.030 --> 35:17.110
When did you arrive at the Cold Spring Palace?

35:29.610 --> 35:31.650
It's none of your business.

35:31.870 --> 35:33.500
I've been thinking

35:34.100 --> 35:36.350
that if Zhen Yu hid Xi like how

35:36.380 --> 35:37.750
he hid Qi Feng's identity,

35:37.810 --> 35:39.770
turning Qi Feng into Chen Ye,

35:39.790 --> 35:41.420
then who would he have turned

35:42.280 --> 35:44.050
my sister Xi into?

35:45.570 --> 35:47.170
Bai Shuo.

35:47.190 --> 35:48.310
You are ridiculous.

35:48.340 --> 35:50.340
Do you think I'm Bai Xi?

35:50.490 --> 35:52.310
Have you forgotten what I've done?

35:52.630 --> 35:53.720
I remember.

35:55.060 --> 35:56.450
I've never forgotten

35:57.560 --> 35:59.180
any of the things

35:59.980 --> 36:01.610
you've done.

36:02.220 --> 36:03.390
So,

36:03.630 --> 36:04.880
how could you

36:04.910 --> 36:07.070
and how dare you have such delusions?

36:07.850 --> 36:13.150
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

36:08.910 --> 36:09.720
Yes.

36:10.710 --> 36:11.820
It's a delusion.

36:11.850 --> 36:13.830
I can't even think about it.

36:14.370 --> 36:16.530
It's a delusion that can never be redeemed.

36:15.880 --> 36:21.340
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

36:17.340 --> 36:19.320
If my Xi is still alive,

36:20.070 --> 36:21.900
if you are her,

36:23.250 --> 36:25.380
I just want to ask why.

36:24.210 --> 36:31.500
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

36:25.960 --> 36:27.370
Why did she become Fu Ling

36:27.440 --> 36:29.630
with so much blood on her hands?

36:30.000 --> 36:32.560
Why did she do all of that to Ning'an City?

36:31.850 --> 36:36.860
♫I'm your wanderer♫

36:32.580 --> 36:35.020
Why did she try to kill me again and again?

36:35.050 --> 36:37.020
Why did she watch...

36:39.630 --> 36:41.220
Watch Father

36:39.870 --> 36:44.180
♫The flowers flew away♫

36:42.300 --> 36:44.230
die in front of her?

36:47.570 --> 36:51.450
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

36:49.460 --> 36:51.150
If you aren't her,

36:52.470 --> 36:54.100
why are you silent?

36:55.660 --> 37:02.930
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

36:56.000 --> 36:57.480
You care this much about

36:57.480 --> 36:58.690
that Bai Xi who died a long time ago?

36:58.730 --> 37:00.590
You care so much that even if I killed your father,

37:00.590 --> 37:02.060
you'd still rather I be her.

37:02.080 --> 37:03.000
Bai Shuo,

37:03.030 --> 37:04.090
if you really need a family,

37:03.490 --> 37:09.130
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

37:04.110 --> 37:05.110
then fine.

37:05.150 --> 37:06.440
Make me the antidote for the Heart Devouring Pill.

37:06.440 --> 37:07.880
Then I can consider being Bai Xi

37:07.880 --> 37:08.910
and grant your wish!

37:19.150 --> 37:20.490
A person like you...

37:23.720 --> 37:25.640
Would never be my Xi.

37:28.610 --> 37:31.890
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

37:33.110 --> 37:35.430
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

37:36.300 --> 37:39.560
♫That year, that year♫

37:39.010 --> 37:40.010
Shuo.

37:40.390 --> 37:43.180
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

37:44.050 --> 37:47.080
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

37:48.300 --> 37:50.770
♫Layer after layer♫

37:51.780 --> 37:54.430
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

37:55.120 --> 37:57.500
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

37:58.340 --> 38:01.890
♫I remember that word of concern♫

38:02.480 --> 38:05.560
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

38:06.410 --> 38:08.920
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

38:08.620 --> 38:09.660
Xi.

38:09.720 --> 38:13.000
♫It dried in the wind♫

38:10.260 --> 38:11.620
It's not your fault.

38:13.550 --> 38:15.390
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

38:14.860 --> 38:16.440
Don't do this to yourself.

38:16.030 --> 38:19.500
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

38:20.390 --> 38:23.510
♫That year, that year♫

38:23.810 --> 38:27.020
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

38:27.720 --> 38:30.790
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

38:32.320 --> 38:34.610
♫Layer after layer♫

38:35.700 --> 38:38.970
♫Another year passed♫

38:43.110 --> 38:47.070
♫Another year passed♫

39:03.990 --> 39:05.650
Why are you waiting here?

39:05.890 --> 39:07.220
I know you well.

39:08.170 --> 39:09.770
Since you suspect

39:09.800 --> 39:11.240
Fu Ling is Bai Xi,

39:11.260 --> 39:13.130
with your personality, you'd definitely ask her.

39:13.970 --> 39:14.880
How is it?

39:15.140 --> 39:16.290
What did she say?

39:17.900 --> 39:19.420
I thought too much.

39:19.450 --> 39:21.050
It's impossible for her to be Xi.

39:21.070 --> 39:22.110
Is it impossible

39:22.810 --> 39:24.130
or do you not want her to be?

39:30.630 --> 39:33.540
In the past, I thought that since we live in the world,

39:31.790 --> 39:35.420
♫The person standing far away♫

39:33.850 --> 39:35.990
we can't live our lives in ignorance.

39:36.200 --> 39:38.660
♫Don't be afraid♫

39:36.370 --> 39:38.120
We should get to the bottom of everything

39:38.520 --> 39:39.870
and ask for the truth.

39:39.270 --> 39:43.210
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

39:41.940 --> 39:44.130
But today, I suddenly feel that

39:44.070 --> 39:50.690
♫Walk towards me♫

39:44.160 --> 39:46.230
perhaps ignorance isn't a bad thing.

39:46.670 --> 39:48.310
I understand how you feel.

39:49.420 --> 39:51.070
Do you know who you're like now?

39:51.990 --> 39:53.520
Like me when I was

39:52.510 --> 39:55.490
♫My heart feels so...♫

39:53.700 --> 39:55.170
facing Qi Feng in the Stone Clan.

39:55.920 --> 40:01.520
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

39:56.040 --> 39:57.730
I understand your unease

39:58.880 --> 40:00.320
and hesitance.

40:03.470 --> 40:07.770
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

40:04.150 --> 40:05.350
Fan Yue,

40:05.450 --> 40:07.580
let's leave here tomorrow.

40:08.080 --> 40:10.090
We came here to find Master.

40:10.140 --> 40:12.010
Now, Master is safe

40:11.180 --> 40:14.640
♫You are my distant call♫

40:12.030 --> 40:13.870
and he doesn't want to leave Bodhi Village.

40:13.900 --> 40:15.460
I can't force him.

40:15.130 --> 40:19.790
♫You are my first and last♫

40:15.860 --> 40:17.260
And Chong Zhao

40:17.290 --> 40:19.080
has reunited with his parents.

40:19.100 --> 40:21.060
There's no need for me to stay any longer.

40:20.230 --> 40:26.260
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

40:21.080 --> 40:22.650
Let's go.

40:22.680 --> 40:24.120
Let's continue collecting Contemplations

40:24.600 --> 40:26.250
and finding Xi,

40:26.450 --> 40:27.740
okay?

40:26.580 --> 40:29.540
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

40:29.440 --> 40:31.130
No matter what decision you make,

40:30.120 --> 40:34.250
♫Let's never let go♫

40:31.880 --> 40:33.500
I'll be with you.

40:49.440 --> 40:51.000
There are only two bedrooms at home.

40:51.020 --> 40:52.240
My parents are in one room.

40:52.270 --> 40:53.520
Only this one is left.

40:54.000 --> 40:55.040
You sleep on the bed.

40:55.060 --> 40:56.390
I'll sleep on the floor.

40:57.300 --> 40:58.330
Chong Zhao,

40:59.190 --> 41:01.230
let's stay in Bodhi Village, okay?

41:02.560 --> 41:05.190
You've been separated from your parents for so many years.

41:05.210 --> 41:06.360
Let's stay here

41:06.380 --> 41:07.620
to keep them company,

41:07.750 --> 41:08.770
okay?

41:12.880 --> 41:14.260
It was just an offhanded comment.

41:14.280 --> 41:15.680
Don't take it to heart.

41:15.700 --> 41:16.410
Tomorrow.

41:16.440 --> 41:17.850
I'll leave tomorrow.

41:23.620 --> 41:25.220
That's not what I meant.

41:26.130 --> 41:28.040
I just feel something is wrong.

41:28.060 --> 41:29.460
What do you mean?

41:29.490 --> 41:31.020
My parents have always hated evil

41:31.080 --> 41:32.690
and viewed protecting humans as their duty.

41:32.720 --> 41:33.960
They'd slain countless demons

41:33.960 --> 41:35.620
under their sword,

41:35.690 --> 41:37.810
but now they're comfortable living here.

41:37.830 --> 41:39.830
They don't care about the fight between immortals and demons anymore.

41:39.970 --> 41:41.300
Can ten years in seclusion

41:41.610 --> 41:42.630
really change someone's

41:42.630 --> 41:44.330
century-old beliefs?

41:44.360 --> 41:47.330
Maybe it's because they'd had a

41:47.350 --> 41:48.790
life-or-death experience.

41:48.810 --> 41:50.190
I hope so.

41:50.790 --> 41:52.210
But didn't you notice?

41:52.290 --> 41:53.880
Since they met me,

41:53.910 --> 41:56.360
they said a lot and explained a lot,

41:56.380 --> 41:58.380
but they never asked me...

42:00.780 --> 42:02.700
How I grew up all these years

42:03.420 --> 42:04.940
or how I've been doing.

42:13.640 --> 42:15.280
What a beautiful night.

42:15.300 --> 42:17.210
You should have a good dream.

42:44.390 --> 42:46.210
You're akin to the stars in the world.

42:46.240 --> 42:47.120
My heart

42:47.140 --> 42:48.400
yearns for you.

42:55.590 --> 42:56.610
Good.

43:02.490 --> 43:03.610
Jing Yuan.

43:03.940 --> 43:05.010
Meeting you

43:05.180 --> 43:06.200
and falling in love with you

43:06.550 --> 43:08.980
is the happiest thing

43:09.010 --> 43:10.710
in my long and boring life.
